# -*-perl-*-

=head1 NAME

BENCHMARK - Basic benchmarking recipe

=head1 DESCRIPTION

Basic realistic recipe suitable for benchmarking tests. Processes
DREAM/STARE images.

=head1 KNOWN ISSUES

This primitive can not handle time series observing modes.

=head1 AUTHOR

Andy Gibb E<lt>agg@astro.ubc.caE<gt>,
Tim Jenness E<lt>t.jenness@jach.hawaii.eduE<gt>

